1
00:00:49,719 --> 00:00:51,119
The scene here is lively right now,

2
00:00:51,679 --> 00:00:53,200
but looking back,

3
00:00:53,200 --> 00:00:54,320
the toughest moment,

4
00:00:54,960 --> 00:00:55,640
when exactly was it?

5
00:00:56,200 --> 00:00:57,520
It was when we'd just arrived in Changzhou,

6
00:00:57,520 --> 00:00:59,039
about two or three months in.

7
00:00:59,640 --> 00:01:01,719
The wind was really strong that day,

8
00:01:01,880 --> 00:01:02,320
and it was freezing.

9
00:01:02,439 --> 00:01:04,040
We were at the stall holding our kid,

10
00:01:05,239 --> 00:01:06,239
and I just wondered,

11
00:01:07,640 --> 00:01:09,280
how could life ever get better?

12
00:01:10,239 --> 00:01:11,359
Maybe we should hang in there a bit longer.

13
00:01:12,480 --> 00:01:14,560
And then, our wait paid off.

14
00:01:14,560 --> 00:01:15,760
He came to our stall.

15
00:01:16,680 --> 00:01:17,400
At that moment, it felt like

16
00:01:17,400 --> 00:01:18,560
a ray of light shone in.

17
00:01:18,840 --> 00:01:19,799
He not only said

18
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,599
our skewers were delicious,

19
00:01:21,879 --> 00:01:23,519
but he also encouraged us

20
00:01:23,519 --> 00:01:24,439
to keep going.

21
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:25,959
He believed that we,

22
00:01:25,959 --> 00:01:27,599
with our genuine food, in Changzhou,

23
00:01:27,599 --> 00:01:29,920
would definitely survive

24
00:01:29,920 --> 00:01:31,640
and thrive.

25
00:01:32,439 --> 00:01:33,000
I heard

26
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:34,359
he even posted on his WeChat Moments

27
00:01:35,239 --> 00:01:36,079
and called up

28
00:01:36,079 --> 00:01:37,920
a bunch of his buddies to come eat.

29
00:01:37,920 --> 00:01:39,239
A dozen or so showed up at once.

30
00:01:39,760 --> 00:01:40,640
Is that also the reason

31
00:01:40,840 --> 00:01:41,840
why someone like you, who doesn't play,

32
00:01:42,040 --> 00:01:44,200
decided to sponsor the Jiangsu Super League?

33
00:01:45,560 --> 00:01:47,280
Later on, we heard about

34
00:01:47,280 --> 00:01:48,560
this Jiangsu Super League thing,

35
00:01:48,560 --> 00:01:50,439
and we learned that at the time,

36
00:01:50,840 --> 00:01:52,560
it might need some help.

37
00:01:52,840 --> 00:01:53,879
Just like us back then,

38
00:01:53,879 --> 00:01:54,640
exactly the same.

39
00:01:55,079 --> 00:01:56,359
They also needed a little help.

40
00:01:57,000 --> 00:01:57,680
Maybe what we

41
00:01:57,680 --> 00:01:59,120
can do is very little,

42
00:01:59,200 --> 00:02:00,879
and the effort we can make is small,

43
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:02,439
but I still hope

44
00:02:02,760 --> 00:02:04,200
I can become a seed

45
00:02:04,599 --> 00:02:05,359
that sparks a prairie fire.

46
00:02:13,080 --> 00:02:13,639
What are you doing?

47
00:02:13,759 --> 00:02:14,199
What's going on?

48
00:02:14,199 --> 00:02:14,719
What's this about?

49
00:02:15,280 --> 00:02:16,120
Watch where you're going!

50
00:02:17,680 --> 00:02:18,120
Stop it!

51
00:02:19,639 --> 00:02:20,520
Xiao Liu, pull over, quick!

52
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:22,400
Are the players fighting?

53
00:02:28,199 --> 00:02:28,719
What happened?

54
00:02:29,719 --> 00:02:30,280
What are you doing?

55
00:02:31,039 --> 00:02:31,680
What's going on? What's going on?

56
00:02:32,080 --> 00:02:33,280
Come on, come on.

57
00:02:33,280 --> 00:02:33,960
The media's here too.

58
00:02:34,520 --> 00:02:35,479
Go on, keep it up in front of them!

59
00:02:36,039 --> 00:02:36,599
Keep going!

60
00:02:37,240 --> 00:02:37,800
Lao Huang.

61
00:02:38,520 --> 00:02:39,000
Da Peng.

62
00:02:40,120 --> 00:02:41,120
I know everyone right now

63
00:02:41,120 --> 00:02:41,719
is really frustrated.

64
00:02:42,719 --> 00:02:43,719
But it's exactly at times like this

65
00:02:43,719 --> 00:02:44,960
that we need to stay calm,

66
00:02:45,479 --> 00:02:46,759
and to stay united.

67
00:02:47,319 --> 00:02:48,599
The person I just interviewed

68
00:02:48,599 --> 00:02:49,000
was saying

69
00:02:49,400 --> 00:02:50,280
that Changzhou FC

70
00:02:50,280 --> 00:02:51,639
is getting better day by day.

71
00:02:52,159 --> 00:02:52,599
Really.

72
00:02:53,360 --> 00:02:53,840
Coach.

73
00:02:54,479 --> 00:02:55,879
Could I borrow everyone for a moment?

74
00:02:56,280 --> 00:02:58,120
I brought some things today.

75
00:02:58,680 --> 00:02:59,639
I'd like to show them to you.

76
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,879
Let's go to the meeting room.

77
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:02,759
Is that okay?

78
00:03:06,000 --> 00:03:06,680
Trust me.

79
00:03:13,599 --> 00:03:14,280
Have you guys been reading

80
00:03:14,280 --> 00:03:15,240
the comments online?

81
00:03:15,800 --> 00:03:16,599
Have you seen the messages?

82
00:03:17,879 --> 00:03:18,520
Some of them.

83
00:03:19,120 --> 00:03:20,199
We put together a collection

84
00:03:20,240 --> 00:03:21,199
of online comments and messages.

85
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:21,800
Let's take a look.

86
00:03:22,199 --> 00:03:22,759
Look at this first one.

87
00:03:23,120 --> 00:03:23,520
It says,

88
00:03:23,759 --> 00:03:24,800
"Even though they lost,

89
00:03:25,080 --> 00:03:26,280
when Li Xiaoyong made that

90
00:03:26,280 --> 00:03:27,199
sixty-meter sprint,

91
00:03:27,599 --> 00:03:28,560
it brought me to tears."

92
00:03:29,280 --> 00:03:29,960
This very moment,

93
00:03:29,960 --> 00:03:30,639
I noticed it too.

94
00:03:31,039 --> 00:03:32,039
Right before the final whistle,

95
00:03:32,599 --> 00:03:33,479
our Captain Li Xiaoyong

96
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:35,120
was still rallying the team,

97
00:03:35,120 --> 00:03:36,400
launching another attack.

98
00:03:36,680 --> 00:03:38,719
Our boss said, just for that spirit alone,

99
00:03:38,919 --> 00:03:40,000
when our company hires next year,

100
00:03:40,000 --> 00:03:42,080
Changzhou natives get priority.

101
00:03:42,280 --> 00:03:42,840
Thanks, Xiaoyong.

102
00:03:43,360 --> 00:03:44,840
You speak for all true Changzhou men.

103
00:03:45,000 --> 00:03:45,599
Thank you, thank you.

104
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,199
Let's look at the second one.

105
00:03:48,159 --> 00:03:48,719
Look at this one.

106
00:03:48,719 --> 00:03:49,800
It says, "I'm from Yancheng,

107
00:03:50,080 --> 00:03:51,120
but yesterday at the stadium,

108
00:03:51,199 --> 00:03:52,159
I saw that P.E. teacher

109
00:03:52,159 --> 00:03:53,439
from Changzhou cramp up."

110
00:03:54,120 --> 00:03:55,280
Xie the Loudspeaker, is that you?

111
00:03:56,520 --> 00:03:57,719
We caught that moment too.

112
00:03:58,520 --> 00:03:59,360
His leg was injured,

113
00:03:59,719 --> 00:04:00,759
but when he saw the ball coming,

114
00:04:00,759 --> 00:04:02,400
he jumped right off the stretcher.

115
00:04:03,280 --> 00:04:04,120
I told everyone at

116
00:04:04,120 --> 00:04:04,919
our Yancheng fan club,

117
00:04:05,000 --> 00:04:05,840
"This team

118
00:04:05,960 --> 00:04:06,759
deserves respect."

119
00:04:07,919 --> 00:04:08,919
So a lot of people online

120
00:04:08,919 --> 00:04:09,919
have noticed

121
00:04:10,520 --> 00:04:11,639
that our Changzhou FC players

122
00:04:11,639 --> 00:04:12,520
are playing

123
00:04:12,680 --> 00:04:13,319
through injuries.

124
00:04:14,400 --> 00:04:15,280
Let's look at the third one.

125
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,560
This is a student studying abroad.

126
00:04:17,040 --> 00:04:17,600
It says,

127
00:04:17,879 --> 00:04:19,519
"Every time I watch a Changzhou FC match,

128
00:04:19,519 --> 00:04:20,600
I have to get up before dawn.

129
00:04:21,240 --> 00:04:22,279
My roommate always asks me,

130
00:04:22,839 --> 00:04:24,160
'Why support a team

131
00:04:24,160 --> 00:04:25,240
that always loses?'"

132
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:26,439
He says,

133
00:04:27,040 --> 00:04:28,480
"Because they look just like me,

134
00:04:28,600 --> 00:04:30,160
struggling in a foreign land,

135
00:04:30,439 --> 00:04:33,120
and always hitting the wall."

136
00:04:40,800 --> 00:04:41,600
Actually, yesterday

137
00:04:42,519 --> 00:04:44,199
I also caught on camera

138
00:04:44,720 --> 00:04:46,560
a five-year-old kid with leukemia.

139
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:47,879
He was there,

140
00:04:47,879 --> 00:04:48,800
holding a cheering stick,

141
00:04:49,120 --> 00:04:50,120
shouting from the sidelines,

142
00:04:50,639 --> 00:04:51,920
'Go Changzhou FC!

143
00:04:52,319 --> 00:04:53,480
Go Changzhou FC!'

144
00:04:54,519 --> 00:04:55,439
The child's father

145
00:04:56,160 --> 00:04:57,040
said on the sidelines,

146
00:04:58,560 --> 00:04:59,279
'It was you,

147
00:04:59,959 --> 00:05:01,240
all of you on the field,

148
00:05:01,639 --> 00:05:02,879
fighting until the very last moment,

149
00:05:02,879 --> 00:05:04,319
never giving up,

150
00:05:04,839 --> 00:05:05,879
that gave my child

151
00:05:06,240 --> 00:05:08,360
the courage to fight his illness.'

152
00:05:09,439 --> 00:05:09,959
You see,

153
00:05:10,279 --> 00:05:11,639
hasn't this transcended winning and losing?

154
00:05:11,639 --> 00:05:12,680
Transcended football itself?

155
00:05:13,279 --> 00:05:13,839
His father said,

156
00:05:13,839 --> 00:05:15,319
'This is the cry of life!'

157
00:05:21,680 --> 00:05:23,160
So the 0-5 you all saw

158
00:05:23,160 --> 00:05:24,120
is just a score.

159
00:05:24,600 --> 00:05:25,120
But these things,

160
00:05:25,720 --> 00:05:26,160
and the stories

161
00:05:26,160 --> 00:05:27,000
I just mentioned,

162
00:05:27,439 --> 00:05:28,439
they're about people's hearts.

163
00:05:29,920 --> 00:05:32,199
And there's Dongha Barbecue.

164
00:05:32,279 --> 00:05:33,560
The story of its owner, Bai Na.

165
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:36,079
We filmed a billboard on the sidelines,

166
00:05:36,079 --> 00:05:37,759
a yellow sign that really stood out.

167
00:05:38,160 --> 00:05:39,639
It read 'Dongha Barbecue.'

168
00:05:40,279 --> 00:05:42,040
And in our stadium,

169
00:05:42,120 --> 00:05:43,160
it was especially eye-catching,

170
00:05:44,040 --> 00:05:45,439
because it was the only one from

171
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:47,879
an ordinary street barbecue joint,

172
00:05:48,240 --> 00:05:49,160
while next to it were

173
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,040
all these major brands.

174
00:05:55,480 --> 00:05:56,160
Are you cold?

175
00:05:56,319 --> 00:05:56,800
No, I'm fine.

176
00:06:05,360 --> 00:06:05,800
Boss

177
00:06:07,279 --> 00:06:07,759
Come on, come on

178
00:06:07,879 --> 00:06:08,480
Give us some skewers

179
00:06:08,720 --> 00:06:09,600
Sure, sure, sure

180
00:06:10,160 --> 00:06:10,920
What would you like?

181
00:06:11,439 --> 00:06:12,360
Anything's fine, just pick some

182
00:06:12,360 --> 00:06:12,680
Whatever's good

183
00:06:12,839 --> 00:06:13,800
How about this bunch?

184
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:14,920
Lamb, beef, pork belly

185
00:06:15,199 --> 00:06:15,519
Sounds good

186
00:06:15,839 --> 00:06:16,279
Alright

187
00:06:19,839 --> 00:06:20,439
I'll grill them up for you

188
00:06:22,000 --> 00:06:22,600
Add some of these too.

189
00:06:22,839 --> 00:06:23,240
This one.

190
00:06:23,399 --> 00:06:23,680
Got it.

191
00:06:24,360 --> 00:06:24,639
Coming right up!

192
00:06:29,399 --> 00:06:30,800
It's pretty cold today

193
00:06:31,319 --> 00:06:32,720
Yeah, the wind is really strong

194
00:06:40,160 --> 00:06:41,120
Here you go

195
00:06:41,240 --> 00:06:42,160
Try it, see if the seasoning's right

196
00:06:48,560 --> 00:06:49,000
How is it?

197
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:49,959
Tasty?

198
00:06:51,959 --> 00:06:52,360
Delicious

199
00:06:53,079 --> 00:06:53,720
Seriously delicious.

200
00:06:54,560 --> 00:06:54,879
Ma'am

201
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:55,639
Sir

202
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,120
You're not from around here, are you?

203
00:06:57,199 --> 00:06:58,720
We just came from the Northeast

204
00:06:58,959 --> 00:07:00,199
Business hasn't been great.

205
00:07:00,759 --> 00:07:01,240
We just got here

206
00:07:01,879 --> 00:07:03,240
As long as the food's good, you'll be fine.

207
00:07:03,519 --> 00:07:03,959
Honestly

208
00:07:04,519 --> 00:07:05,879
compared to our local barbecue,

209
00:07:05,879 --> 00:07:06,839
yours is way better

210
00:07:06,959 --> 00:07:07,480
Really

211
00:07:08,079 --> 00:07:09,680
It's because I love eating it myself

212
00:07:09,720 --> 00:07:11,120
I season and grill everything

213
00:07:11,120 --> 00:07:11,759
to my own taste.

214
00:07:12,720 --> 00:07:13,399
We love it.

215
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:14,439
Then that's what counts.

216
00:07:14,639 --> 00:07:15,600
You've got to keep at it

217
00:07:16,000 --> 00:07:16,519
Ma'am

218
00:07:16,720 --> 00:07:17,759
As long as the food's good

219
00:07:18,399 --> 00:07:20,759
your business will definitely grow

220
00:07:20,920 --> 00:07:22,240
Okay, thank you, thank you

221
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:23,439
Pack up the rest for me, please

222
00:07:23,439 --> 00:07:24,079
Sure, sure, sure

223
00:07:25,439 --> 00:07:26,279
A hundred thousand yuan.

224
00:07:26,759 --> 00:07:28,399
A hundred thousand for a billboard like this.

225
00:07:29,439 --> 00:07:31,040
She had to save up for over half a year,

226
00:07:31,279 --> 00:07:32,319
sell thirty thousand skewers,

227
00:07:33,199 --> 00:07:34,959
to sponsor a billboard like this

228
00:07:34,959 --> 00:07:36,360
to support everyone's football dream.

229
00:07:37,120 --> 00:07:37,560
Look

230
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:38,800
Love is flowing around

231
00:07:38,920 --> 00:07:39,360
Isn't it?

232
00:07:39,759 --> 00:07:40,879
Look at these comments

233
00:07:41,000 --> 00:07:41,920
Look at these messages

234
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:43,680
Look at the people supporting us

235
00:07:43,680 --> 00:07:45,240
Even a five-year-old kid with leukemia

236
00:07:45,480 --> 00:07:46,079
Even

237
00:07:46,079 --> 00:07:47,879
the lady running a street barbecue stall.

238
00:07:48,240 --> 00:07:48,879
Seeing them,

239
00:07:49,360 --> 00:07:49,959
we need to stop and think,

240
00:07:50,480 --> 00:07:51,920
how many people across China

241
00:07:52,480 --> 00:07:53,839
see themselves in all of you,

242
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:55,639
seeing their own reflection.

243
00:07:57,680 --> 00:07:58,759
How do we repay

244
00:07:58,879 --> 00:08:00,160
the fans for their support?

245
00:08:02,160 --> 00:08:03,240
It's really hard to keep going

246
00:08:04,040 --> 00:08:05,079
When you can't hold on anymore

247
00:08:05,079 --> 00:08:05,439
what do you do?

248
00:08:06,600 --> 00:08:07,959
When Bai Na couldn't hold on anymore

249
00:08:07,959 --> 00:08:08,920
she said something

250
00:08:08,920 --> 00:08:10,079
that hit me really hard

251
00:08:10,759 --> 00:08:11,120
She said

252
00:08:12,879 --> 00:08:14,279
it's not that you see hope

253
00:08:14,959 --> 00:08:15,879
and then you persist.

254
00:08:17,000 --> 00:08:18,319
It's because you persist

255
00:08:19,079 --> 00:08:20,240
that hope appears.

256
00:08:26,040 --> 00:08:27,480
Should we keep going?

257
00:08:28,560 --> 00:08:29,199
We keep going.

258
00:08:32,519 --> 00:08:34,279
Everyone has a lot of opinions

259
00:08:34,279 --> 00:08:34,960
and disagreements, right?

260
00:08:35,120 --> 00:08:36,200
Let's invite everyone up here

261
00:08:36,399 --> 00:08:37,159
to say a few words.

262
00:08:38,000 --> 00:08:38,679
Coach, is that okay with you?

263
00:08:39,159 --> 00:08:39,679
Of course

264
00:08:40,480 --> 00:08:40,919
Then

265
00:08:41,080 --> 00:08:42,200
Lao Xie, Xiaoyong

266
00:08:50,759 --> 00:08:52,080
Honestly, every time in the backfield

267
00:08:52,200 --> 00:08:53,639
when I'm yelling at everyone,

268
00:08:53,960 --> 00:08:55,440
in those conflicts, it's about the play,

269
00:08:55,480 --> 00:08:56,519
not personal.

270
00:08:56,639 --> 00:08:57,759
Don't let him get the ball alone

271
00:08:57,759 --> 00:08:58,360
outside the box.

272
00:08:58,360 --> 00:08:58,960
Outside the box.

273
00:08:59,039 --> 00:08:59,840
If he lines up a shot on me,

274
00:09:00,039 --> 00:09:00,679
it gets really tough.

275
00:09:00,879 --> 00:09:01,919
It's about cutting off his attack.

276
00:09:02,200 --> 00:09:03,759
When you've got more room to move,

277
00:09:03,759 --> 00:09:04,919
you can clear the ball in time

278
00:09:04,919 --> 00:09:06,120
or catch it in your hands.

279
00:09:50,840 --> 00:09:51,559
Lao Chang,

280
00:09:53,960 --> 00:09:55,240
this Lü Shisanmei

281
00:09:55,799 --> 00:09:57,120
is really something else.

282
00:09:57,279 --> 00:09:58,120
She's not just doing

283
00:09:58,120 --> 00:09:58,960
a news report.

284
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:00,720
She's helping our team

285
00:10:01,159 --> 00:10:02,120
find its soul.

286
00:10:02,720 --> 00:10:03,480
I never imagined

287
00:10:03,679 --> 00:10:04,399
this girl

288
00:10:04,840 --> 00:10:06,200
when it comes to motivating people,

289
00:10:06,600 --> 00:10:07,759
she's better than me, the coach.

290
00:10:07,919 --> 00:10:08,559
Absolutely.

291
00:10:08,799 --> 00:10:09,440
No, no, no.

292
00:10:09,720 --> 00:10:10,279
Don't say that.

293
00:10:10,360 --> 00:10:11,000
Don't say that.

294
00:10:12,320 --> 00:10:13,559
The Dongha Barbecue incident

295
00:10:14,320 --> 00:10:15,360
has blown up online.

296
00:10:15,759 --> 00:10:16,799
Number one on the trending list.

297
00:10:17,120 --> 00:10:19,080
They're saying Changzhou is a city

298
00:10:19,159 --> 00:10:21,000
that makes room for dreams

299
00:10:21,720 --> 00:10:23,879
and for barbecue too,

300
00:10:23,879 --> 00:10:24,759
all in one place.

301
00:10:26,279 --> 00:10:27,039
Changzhou

302
00:10:27,120 --> 00:10:27,799
has gone viral.

303
00:10:29,399 --> 00:10:29,960
See?

304
00:10:30,720 --> 00:10:31,320
Hope

305
00:10:31,759 --> 00:10:32,600
is right here, isn't it?

306
00:10:39,960 --> 00:10:40,720
Have something to eat.

307
00:10:42,279 --> 00:10:43,360
Thanks, honey. Just leave it there.

308
00:10:43,360 --> 00:10:44,120
I'll eat in a bit.

309
00:10:44,720 --> 00:10:45,480
Eat it while it's hot.

310
00:10:45,879 --> 00:10:46,600
Okay, I got it.

311
00:10:46,600 --> 00:10:47,120
Just put it down there.

312
00:10:47,120 --> 00:10:47,960
I'll definitely eat it soon.

313
00:10:54,799 --> 00:10:55,440
You know,

314
00:10:55,559 --> 00:10:56,360
I really regret

315
00:10:57,759 --> 00:10:59,360
letting you cover the Jiangsu Super League.

316
00:11:01,000 --> 00:11:01,960
How long has it been since I've seen you?

317
00:11:02,919 --> 00:11:03,600
Even our kid says

318
00:11:03,919 --> 00:11:05,559
he has to watch TV to see his mom.

319
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:08,080
Honey, when you say that,

320
00:11:08,080 --> 00:11:09,320
I start to feel guilty too.

321
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,320
That's exactly the point.

322
00:11:11,399 --> 00:11:12,080
So what should I do?

323
00:11:12,480 --> 00:11:13,799
Just hurry up and eat your noodles.

324
00:11:15,759 --> 00:11:16,840
Okay, I'll eat.

325
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:21,919
Egg noodles.

326
00:11:24,279 --> 00:11:25,039
Actually,

327
00:11:25,519 --> 00:11:26,159
our kid and I

328
00:11:26,440 --> 00:11:27,639
are both really proud of you.

329
00:11:28,480 --> 00:11:30,000
We just don't want you to work too hard.

330
00:11:30,919 --> 00:11:31,720
Honey, I think

331
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:33,000
the way the Jiangsu Super League is going,

332
00:11:33,600 --> 00:11:34,840
it's not just a match for the players,

333
00:11:35,200 --> 00:11:37,360
it's a battlefield for all of Changzhou.

334
00:11:37,840 --> 00:11:39,480
Victory is just ahead.

335
00:11:39,960 --> 00:11:40,639
Alright, alright.

336
00:11:40,639 --> 00:11:41,440
Just hurry up and eat your noodles.

337
00:11:42,399 --> 00:11:42,840
So good.

338
00:11:42,840 --> 00:11:43,399
Do you want a bite?

339
00:11:43,480 --> 00:11:44,240
I've eaten, I've eaten already.

340
00:11:44,240 --> 00:11:44,679
You eat.

341
00:11:44,919 --> 00:11:45,879
Is this fried egg enough?

342
00:11:46,120 --> 00:11:47,320
Number four in the midfield

343
00:11:47,320 --> 00:11:48,200
will definitely stick to you tight.

344
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:49,799
Then you need to wait for your chance.

345
00:11:50,240 --> 00:11:52,000
You need to push forward quickly, wait for number four...

346
00:11:58,399 --> 00:11:59,080
Hello, Sister Yan.

347
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,519
Xiaoyong, where are you?

348
00:12:01,919 --> 00:12:03,360
Coach wants you to come down to the shop.

349
00:12:05,840 --> 00:12:06,360
Sister Yan,

350
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,200
I'm right in the middle of—

351
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:11,519
Okay, okay, I'll be right over.

352
00:12:13,679 --> 00:12:14,720
If Sister Yan's calling you,

353
00:12:14,840 --> 00:12:15,919
it must be something more important

354
00:12:15,919 --> 00:12:16,639
than football.

355
00:12:17,159 --> 00:12:17,639
Hurry up and go.

356
00:12:20,360 --> 00:12:20,759
I'm going.

357
00:12:26,279 --> 00:12:26,679
Here.

358
00:12:27,519 --> 00:12:27,960
Try some.

359
00:12:28,320 --> 00:12:29,120
Thanks, Sister Yan.

360
00:12:35,879 --> 00:12:36,399
How is it?

361
00:12:37,039 --> 00:12:38,279
Are the noodles good today?

362
00:12:39,799 --> 00:12:40,399
Really delicious.

363
00:12:41,519 --> 00:12:42,679
Building a life together

364
00:12:42,879 --> 00:12:44,279
is just like eating.

365
00:12:44,799 --> 00:12:46,759
What suits your taste is the best.

366
00:12:52,399 --> 00:12:53,240
You little rascal,

367
00:12:53,240 --> 00:12:54,360
did you already guess why

368
00:12:54,360 --> 00:12:55,159
I called you here today?

369
00:12:58,399 --> 00:12:59,080
You know,

370
00:12:59,679 --> 00:13:01,320
stop using your male mindset

371
00:13:01,320 --> 00:13:02,360
to second-guess Lu Yao.

372
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:04,360
That girl Lu Yao

373
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:05,200
loves you.

374
00:13:05,639 --> 00:13:06,679
And she sincerely wants

375
00:13:06,679 --> 00:13:07,600
to build a life together with you.

376
00:13:08,039 --> 00:13:09,399
Have you forgotten, when Coach Chang and I

377
00:13:09,399 --> 00:13:10,240
first got together,

378
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:12,000
he had nothing back then.

379
00:13:12,320 --> 00:13:13,399
His football career went nowhere,

380
00:13:13,559 --> 00:13:14,480
he didn't have much money either.

381
00:13:14,919 --> 00:13:15,840
So what?

382
00:13:16,679 --> 00:13:17,960
Do you remember when you were little,

383
00:13:18,240 --> 00:13:19,120
the two of us

384
00:13:19,120 --> 00:13:19,720
squeezed into

385
00:13:19,720 --> 00:13:20,960
that ten-square-meter dorm room?

386
00:13:21,320 --> 00:13:22,080
When we had no money,

387
00:13:22,399 --> 00:13:23,200
I ate noodles with him

388
00:13:23,200 --> 00:13:24,120
for a whole month.

389
00:13:24,639 --> 00:13:25,639
Times are different now.

390
00:13:29,639 --> 00:13:30,519
I don't want Lu Yao

391
00:13:30,519 --> 00:13:31,080
to suffer along with me.

392
00:13:39,720 --> 00:13:41,000
In today's society,

393
00:13:42,519 --> 00:13:44,080
the foundation of marriage is built

394
00:13:44,080 --> 00:13:45,320
on financial stability.

395
00:13:51,720 --> 00:13:52,759
What's between the two of us,

396
00:13:52,759 --> 00:13:53,559
please stay out of it.

397
00:13:55,440 --> 00:13:56,039
I'm heading back now.

398
00:13:56,759 --> 00:13:57,399
You stand right there!

399
00:13:59,840 --> 00:14:00,799
Now I get it.

400
00:14:01,240 --> 00:14:02,440
It's not that you don't trust Lu Yao.

401
00:14:02,879 --> 00:14:04,200
You don't trust yourself.

402
00:14:14,600 --> 00:14:15,080
Yeah.

403
00:14:17,159 --> 00:14:18,559
I really don't believe in myself.

404
00:14:21,159 --> 00:14:22,120
Sister Yan, you know what?

405
00:14:22,120 --> 00:14:23,200
That little gift she once mentioned

406
00:14:23,200 --> 00:14:23,919
in passing,

407
00:14:25,720 --> 00:14:27,080
I had to work three jobs for a month,

408
00:14:27,080 --> 00:14:27,799
scrimping and saving,

409
00:14:27,799 --> 00:14:28,679
just to afford it.

410
00:14:29,919 --> 00:14:31,320
I don't want her to suffer with me.

411
00:14:32,759 --> 00:14:33,600
I don't want her

412
00:14:33,600 --> 00:14:34,480
living with me in a rental.

413
00:14:35,279 --> 00:14:36,240
I don't want her, on rainy days,

414
00:14:36,240 --> 00:14:37,080
after getting off work,

415
00:14:37,080 --> 00:14:38,200
to still ride the bus with me.

416
00:14:38,320 --> 00:14:39,559
I don't want her to marry

417
00:14:39,559 --> 00:14:40,200
a failure,

418
00:14:40,200 --> 00:14:41,399
and have a failed life.

419
00:14:41,720 --> 00:14:42,480
In your mind,

420
00:14:42,840 --> 00:14:44,000
is living an ordinary life

421
00:14:44,000 --> 00:14:44,919
really a failure?

422
00:14:52,759 --> 00:14:53,360
Xiaoyong.

423
00:14:54,840 --> 00:14:55,679
Tell Sister Yan,

424
00:14:57,039 --> 00:14:58,279
do you love her or not?

425
00:15:05,320 --> 00:15:05,799
I do.

426
00:15:19,120 --> 00:15:20,159
Like I always say,

427
00:15:20,879 --> 00:15:22,919
building a life together is like eating.

428
00:15:23,399 --> 00:15:25,240
Whatever suits your taste is the best.

429
00:15:27,279 --> 00:15:28,200
Do you know

430
00:15:28,200 --> 00:15:29,000
who made this bowl of noodles?

431
00:15:58,399 --> 00:15:59,639
I don't think being with you

432
00:15:59,639 --> 00:16:00,840
means a failed life.

433
00:16:02,159 --> 00:16:03,080
And I don't think

434
00:16:03,360 --> 00:16:04,279
losing a football match

435
00:16:04,279 --> 00:16:05,039
makes you a failure.

436
00:16:06,120 --> 00:16:06,679
Xiaoyong,

437
00:16:07,480 --> 00:16:08,840
I just think you lack confidence.

438
00:16:09,240 --> 00:16:10,200
You run from your problems.

439
00:16:10,559 --> 00:16:11,519
That's what's a failure.

440
00:16:12,840 --> 00:16:14,279
That's also the failure of our relationship.

441
00:16:21,279 --> 00:16:22,720
I wanted to play in the Jiangsu Super League

442
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,120
to fulfill my childhood dream.

443
00:16:25,879 --> 00:16:26,919
I really didn't expect

444
00:16:27,639 --> 00:16:28,519
that this one shot

445
00:16:29,759 --> 00:16:30,759
would kick all my confidence away.

446
00:16:34,320 --> 00:16:35,039
Yeah,

447
00:16:36,320 --> 00:16:38,120
you almost kicked me away too.

448
00:16:43,200 --> 00:16:43,559
Yaoyao.

449
00:16:45,639 --> 00:16:46,320
I'm sorry.

450
00:16:49,919 --> 00:16:50,639
Sorry for what?

451
00:16:52,480 --> 00:16:53,200
I was wrong to

452
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:54,240
shut myself off

453
00:16:55,399 --> 00:16:56,200
and act like an ostrich.

454
00:16:57,440 --> 00:16:58,039
What else?

455
00:16:59,200 --> 00:17:00,399
I was wrong to run away

456
00:17:00,399 --> 00:17:01,039
whenever problems came up.

457
00:17:02,679 --> 00:17:03,600
I should keep pushing on.

458
00:17:04,799 --> 00:17:05,559
What else?

459
00:17:09,640 --> 00:17:11,799
I was wrong to push you away

460
00:17:12,119 --> 00:17:12,960
and hurt you.

461
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:14,279
And?

462
00:17:17,759 --> 00:17:18,799
Okay, okay, enough.

463
00:17:18,799 --> 00:17:19,640
I get it.

464
00:17:22,400 --> 00:17:23,359
All right, then.

465
00:17:25,000 --> 00:17:26,119
As for me,

466
00:17:26,319 --> 00:17:27,799
for this period,

467
00:17:27,920 --> 00:17:29,319
I'll generously

468
00:17:29,599 --> 00:17:31,960
leave you to Changzhou FC.
